    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You gain the following benefits.</p><p><strong>Ability Score Increase.</strong> Increase your Intelligence, Wisdom, or Charisma score by 1, to a maximum of 30.</p><p><strong>Free Casting.</strong> Whenever you cast a spell with a level 1-4 spell slot, roll [[/r 1d4]]. If the number you roll is the same as the slot's level, the slot isn't expended.</p><section id=\"secret-KMAFFZCOzi6Cuemh\" class=\"secret\"><p><strong>Foundry Note</strong></p><p>If the number is the same, uncheck the Consumption option when using the spell.</p></section>",
